          "title": "What Counts as PHI?",
          "type": "poster",
          "x": 8,
          "y": 1,
          "fact": "PHI includes 18 types of identifiers: names, dates, phone numbers, email, SSN, medical record numbers, health plan IDs, account numbers, license/plate numbers, device IDs, URLs, IPs, biometrics, photos, and any other unique identifier. If it can identify a patient AND relates to their health, treatment, or payment — it's PHI."
