          "title": "The 18 PHI Identifiers",
          "type": "manual",
          "x": 2,
          "y": 8,
          "fact": "Welcome to healthcare, where Protected Health Information (PHI) is more valuable than Bitcoin and twice as regulated. PHI = The Big 18 Identifiers + Health Info. Think: names, addresses, SSNs, medical records, dates of birth, phone numbers, photos, basically anything that could identify a patient AND their health status. The Golden Rule: If you can connect health data to a specific person, congrats—it's PHI. Treat it like it's your own embarrassing medical history."
